iciliana; photo J. Prag 13.05.2016\" src=\"ISic000366_fr1_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000366_fr1_rear.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 13.05.2016\" src=\"ISic000366_fr1_rear-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000366_fr2_rear_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 14.10.2016\" src=\"ISic000366_fr2_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000366_fr2_rear.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 14.10.2016\" src=\"ISic000366_fr2_rear-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":272,"html":273},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based upon photograph, after Korhonen\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":275,"html":276},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>(tomb) of Gaius Pompeius Felix and Scribonia Restituta\u003C/p>  ",{"id":278,"html":279},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Given that both names reflect senatorial families attested in the area, this is assumed to be a freedman and freedwoman of the families. Korhonen notes the absence of 'Dis Manibus' as encouraging a first-century date, alongside the palaeography. Castelli and Ferrara report the right fragment only as a separate text, in addition to reporting the entire text, following a notice in Amico.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":281,"html":282},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliogr