to Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 14.10.2016\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#AA\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>C\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ai\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> Po\u003Cunclear>m\u003C/unclear>pei Felic\u003Chi rend=\"small\">i\u003C/hi>s\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>et Sc\u003Cunclear>r\u003C/unclear>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ib\u003C/supplied>oniae \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> Resti\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\" break=\"no\"/>\u003Cunclear>t\u003C/unclear>utae \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text based upon photograph, after Korhonen\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>(tomb) of Gaius Pompeius Felix and Scribonia Restituta\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>Given that both names reflect senatorial families attested in the area, this is assumed to be a freedman and freedwoman of the families. Korhonen notes the absence of 'Dis Manibus' as encouraging a first-century date, alongside the palaeography. Castelli and Ferrara report the right fragment only as a separate text, in addition to reporting the entire text, following a notice in Amico.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl 